{"tid":349878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫北者欲返回北韓　「在南韓受到糞土般對待」","createTime":"2017-08-07T00:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T11:16:14.000Z","uid":1886,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13cc8bcf1151e5b4aa2a9066cef7203ded14fcbe","tid":349878,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">北韓對外界來說是一座神秘的囚牢，但有北韓人歷盡艱辛成功脫北後，指在南韓的待遇有如二等公民，連薪金亦遭到剝削，反而渴望回鄉，又指為北韓的核武發展自豪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170806/large/1502025422_be49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170806%2Flarge%2F1502025422_be49.jpg&h=1b180413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170806&amp;guid=57049474&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170806%26guid%3D57049474%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=7uKelBNRfzH3e%2FejPrgbUosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=fdc012b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170806%26guid%3D57049474%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=62162e6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170806&amp;guid=57049474&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a></div>"},{"pid":"4b991b57a69b282273346e4381b2b90a8114466d","tid":349878,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"2014年44歲的權哲男（Kwon Chol-nam，音譯）偷渡中國後，經中國蛇頭安排徒步穿過老撾叢林抵達泰國，再飛往南韓展開新生活。不過，他表示：「你騎上一匹馬後方知牠是否適合你，我試過了，南韓不適合我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我想回到北韓與我的妻子和16歲兒子團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170806/large/1502025425_4803.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170806%2Flarge%2F1502025425_4803.jpg&h=76a65510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「他們直呼我的名字，如弱智一樣對待我，甚至同工不同酬。」他經常被嘲笑連一些當地常用的基本英文詞彙也不懂，只能從事農業和建築業工作。他在生活和事業均不如意下，倍感思念仍身處北韓的妻兒，儲下辛苦錢寄給他們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又經常上網看北韓的政治宣傳片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月，當權哲男指判頭未有如約給他搬運磚頭的工資，他終於崩潰，決定申請南韓護照，從而經中國回到北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。翌月他因計劃逃到北韓被捕，羈留多月後被判緩刑1年，其他脫北者漸漸疏離。此後，權哲男曾發起聯署呈交聯合國，並召開記者會爭取各界讓他回鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"32c5bea419a14509c49a8d90445c9848575374c3","tid":349878,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"權哲男明白縱使回到北韓亦難免被罰勞改，但表示「在北韓，我或許不富有，但我能明白身邊的人，而且不會如在南韓般受到糞土一樣的對待。」<br />\n<br />\n他指<span style=\"color: red;\">回到北韓後，會召開記者</span>會宣告在南韓生活的「真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，去年南韓政府調查指，63%脫北者認為受到社會歧視。"},{"pid":"e92092f6ab286174010cb31c786bda5df0719f26","tid":349878,"uid":80966,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e6af0c6f728ff0d56bb5d303895e051449489f2","tid":349878,"uid":60655,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:39:52.000Z","msg":"北韓人滾回北韓"},{"pid":"909f0342d3c6b3a8dfb4750ba99074f460b6afc5","tid":349878,"uid":2914,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces